title: Did Sarah Palin say: "We had already attacked Iran when it was called Iraq? "
subtitle: "It's like when Bov Papa changed his name to P Diddy, he also said Palin. "You're not fooling anyone, Iraq."
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: In June 2019, Sarah Palin asserted that the United States "has already attacked Iran when it called itself Iraq."
